type="local"
href="jms-00CW.xml"
addr="jms-00CW"
title="Forester 3.0">Forester 3.0</fr:link> adds proper diagnostics and error messages, via the excellent <fr:link
type="external"
href="https://ocaml.org/p/asai/latest">asai</fr:link> library maintained by <fr:link
type="local"
href="favonia.xml"
addr="favonia"
title="Kuen-Bang Hou (Favonia)">Favonia</fr:link>. When something goes wrong in your forest, the terminal output should expain what happened while displaying the precise location in your source file.</fr:p></fr:mainmatter><fr:backmatter /></fr:tree><fr:tree
