text="Custom static assets directories">Custom static assets directories</fr:title><fr:taxon>Feature</fr:taxon><fr:date><fr:year>2023</fr:year><fr:month>12</fr:month><fr:day>15</fr:day></fr:date><fr:authors><fr:author><fr:link
